{"tid":1041063,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】「幣少爺」黃鉦傑涉嫌串謀詐騙被警方拘捕","createTime":"2019-02-28T14:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T19:39:37.000Z","uid":66271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea41f27a24d9c6e3f572868304e7134691f5b342","tid":1041063,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190228/photo/bkn-20190228213554198-0228_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190228220616\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190228%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190228213554198-0228_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190228220616&h=d87ca90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]疑與去年尾深水埗天台撒錢事件有關而聲名大噪的「幣少爺」黃鉦傑，懷疑捲入投資者向他購買虛擬貨幣挖礦機的錢銀糾紛，警方商業罪案調查科經調查後，以涉嫌串謀詐騙拘捕兩名男子，據悉，其中一人為黃鉦傑，警方目前在黃位於荃灣的辦公室及西貢寓所搜查，將於稍後交代案情。[/img]"},{"pid":"ee911fbaa14d6586ee6937e4ff3bbab6927035d0","tid":1041063,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"File coin又要暴跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d91271d80b992d6890ad06235a8ec23cef0cbb","tid":1041063,"uid":231472,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee911fbaa14d6586ee6937e4ff3bbab6927035d0","tid":1041063,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"File coin又要暴跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"仲有得跌？"},{"pid":"c6d5e92b725bb3046ac02bfc6477de58281efdd4","tid":1041063,"uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"要沽2018撲水打官司?"},{"pid":"cfffe4ee1b69dbc5958d3786161f8672b25e511b","tid":1041063,"uid":116033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被